name: Rick
line: Yeah. I mean, you know, it's not like he could have actually done it.

name: Rick
line: Well, duh doy, son. I know you're a child, but the fact that you're trying to use this to justify your own assasination speaks to the necessity of assimilation.

name: Agent
line: Dad, the name’s real, and it’ll probably come up organically in some way later in life. I’m just saying, the two of you made me a little sad to hear this.

name: Rick
line: Well it makes you a little smarter, doesn’t it?

name: Rick
line: I’ve heard a lot about you today. Your family is crazy about you. Your daughter holds you in very high regard. Your job is to be a whistle!

name: Agent
line: Yeah, I guess I shoulda’d put my faith in the right Morty.

name: Rick
line: You should put your faith in your work, Morty. You’re a real solid pickle.

name: Rick
line: You say… that… that’am a three…
